Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.49,0:00:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到  你竟然會深陷迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強的靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喰靈白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承它的土宮一家　真是礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我竟然有種羡慕的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  不管哪邊  今日都得做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂紅蓮  咆哮波
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…別打了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你們…求求你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂  趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就由我來做你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…爸爸他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺生石…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯綱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…是我害死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下不了手…所以害死了他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諫山黃泉是受到殺生石的影響怨靈化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺生石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾狐的靈魂碎片  純粹的妖力結晶體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦為人所獲  在得到無限靈力的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會漸漸被啃噬掉靈魂  而化作怨靈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後與九尾狐的怨念同化  開始毀滅世上的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諫山冥的事件可能也與殺生石有關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是真的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是因為我們將黃泉逼得太緊  她才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什麼理由  接受殺生石都是不可原諒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她則犯了這一禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都做了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…怎麼會…怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死都做不到嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持警戒狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有特異點出現立刻報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室長  靈氣壓地圖反應異常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一觀測班  第二觀測班  全都沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有第三觀測班發來靈氣訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了不讓我們發現行蹤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即向第三觀測班發出退避勸告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室長…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環境省  超自然災害對策室處理班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急出動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯綱  出動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯綱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這樣子去了也是送死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果下定決心了就過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話…父親你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是我太不成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  擅離職守
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御靈解放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:45.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;5;0;35,（咒文大意：不動明王慈救咒  曩莫三曼多縛日羅赧 戰拏摩訶路灑拏 薩頗吒也 吽 怛羅迦 悍漫）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}namah samanta vajrânâm canda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}mahâ rosana sphataya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}hûm traka hâm mâm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來…已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡正在掙脫封印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:11:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是我的力量能夠控制的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  殺生石不是能恢復的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是經過封印處理後的小碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復這種傷勢要消耗很多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就會魂飛魄散  然後死去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前有些話一定要親口對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生於土宮家的人  有著必須繼承喰靈白叡的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而驅使白叡的人都無法長活於世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的媽媽就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後  你也會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓你像你媽媽一樣只能度過短暫的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能夠盡可能活長久些去享受世間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此你只能變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知何時就會撒手人寰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你能儘快成長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年少起就終日修行的日子…必是很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…父親你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的你們的眼睛都已經死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這裡為一語雙關。既指死去的觀測班，又暗示當場的人對黃泉死心之意。）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不能再憑藉靈力來追蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你竟然會成為類型A呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人數不夠嘛  是跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上的人類早晚要被我斬盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:13:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室長！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到還在服役期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你這話是不是有點傷人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死部下也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「原部下」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的人我都親手殺死過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遁入冥府魔道之徒  無論是誰我都不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們非常清楚你所擅長的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想纏住我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭一次和爸爸這樣聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是早點獨當一面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣聊天的機會就能更多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能不知道該和你聊些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪啊  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明是父女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  給我講媽媽的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了…也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…室長！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅槃相會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩端
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…我怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂  愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:17:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂  忘記一切就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最為輕鬆的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步入此道的人都是這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  要想真正變強的話就背負起一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人要想保護別人的話  就不該拋棄回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論那是何等悲慘的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負…一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是一條艱辛坎坷之路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇哪邊全由你決定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂  接著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以！爸爸你還不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經活得足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別了  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室…長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉…呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  亂紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來…選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去了嗎  神樂小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹴師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為你量身定做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新作  名為舞蹴拾三號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹴…拾三號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正了舞蹴拾貳號缺點後誕生的新版本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必定會回應你的靈魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的靈魂…是怎麼想的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話  喰靈  -零-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「祈禱的思慕」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:26.27,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか誓ったのよ　自分の心へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:36.95,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}嘆きの渦にのまれた　君を助けたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:47.67,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重ねる時は変えてゆく　理の歯車が銹びたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:52.66,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}もう戻れない　I hate this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:23:00.26,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}全て壊したい　どこにもまだ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:03.66,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:10.93,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せだったと　あの頃だけ抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:26.42,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}遠ざかる夢の足音　胸に刻み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:26.27,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾經對自己的心靈　許下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:36.95,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要救贖　捲入嘆息漩渦中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:47.67,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交錯的時光轉瞬即逝　道理的齒輪鏽跡斑斕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:52.66,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}已經無法後退　我憎恨此世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:23:00.26,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要摧毀一切　亦無容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:03.66,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:10.93,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將那時僅有的幸福　深情擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:26.42,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}將遠去的夢的足音　刻骨銘心


